episodes.title: Kibamuku Uwabami! Tsui ni Hajimaru Survival Game
episodes.plot: Gan Fall tells the story about the raising of Enel's tyranny, and the vengeance of the Shandian people. Luffy, Zoro, Chopper and Robin escape from a poisonous python.

episodes.title: Sutemi no Haigeki (Reject)! "Senki" Wiper no Kakugo
episodes.plot: The Survival Game begins and Shura is the first to fall. The Shandians split and Wiper meets Luffy. Enel sends the 50 Sacred Warriors. Gan Fall teaches Sanji, Nami, Usopp and Chopper about the power of the Reject Dial.

episodes.title: Kuuchuu no Gekisen! Kaizoku Zoro VS Senshi Braham
episodes.plot: Robin makes it to the ruins and fight against a Sacred Warrior. Zoro faces the lightguns of Braham, while Luffy is still entertained with Wiper. Enel comes into scene.

episodes.title: Unaru Burn Bazooka!! Luffy VS Senki Wiper
episodes.plot: Satori's younger brothers appear to fight against Nami and Gan Fall. Luffy is swallowed by the giant python. Chopper meets the Iron Priest.

episodes.title: Numa no Shiren! Chopper VS Shinkan Gedatsu!!
episodes.plot: Luffy is still trapped into the python, while Robin tries to protect the ruins she found from the powerful attacks of Chief Yama. Chopper must face his fears in order to defeat Priest Gedatsu.

episodes.title: Muteki no Nouryoku! Akasareru Enel no Shoutai
episodes.plot: The Survival Game continues, Gan Fall and Nami defeat Zatori's younger brothers Hotori and Kotori. The former god goes after Enel and Nami is left with his Impact Dial. Conis and Pagaya make it to the Going Merry.

episodes.title: Maburoshi no Miyako! Yuudai Naru Shandra no Iseki!!
episodes.plot: Robin defeats Chief Yama and arrives to the city of Shandora. Zoro makes a new friend. Luffy is starving but still inside the python.

episodes.title: Seizonritsu 0%!! Chopper VS Shinkan Ohm
episodes.plot: Chopper tries to escape from Priest Ohm. Nami and Aisa gets lost in the forest after the giant python spots the Going Merry. Zoro, Gan Fall and Wiper meet Priest Ohm and prepare for the battle.
